# Repository Structure

terraform-aws-server/
├── main.tf                 # Main Terraform configuration
├── variables.tf            # Variable definitions
├── outputs.tf              # Output definitions
├── terraform.tfvars.sample # Sample variables file (rename to terraform.tfvars for use)
├── README.md               # Repository documentation
├── .gitignore              # Git ignore file
├── modules/                # Optional: for more complex configurations
│   └── ec2-instance/       # Optional: EC2 instance module
│       ├── main.tf         # Module configuration
│       ├── variables.tf    # Module variable definitions
│       └── outputs.tf      # Module output definitions
└── examples/               # Optional: example configurations
    └── basic-server/       # Optional: basic server example
        ├── main.tf         # Example configuration
        └── README.md       # Example documentation